data.description: Awesome residential listing with perfect location.  Just minutes to I-20 and not far from the DFW area.  Close to many restaurants and shopping with a rural setting view.  Watch the wildlife at your residence and see the exotic animals roaming the Moncrief Ranch. Great subdivision with large lots. There is no HOA or City Tax. This residence has it all.  It's a great open floorplan with a large kitchen and two dining areas.  This custom home has two separate office areas (or one extra living area) for home offices. This is a large corner lot of 1.2 Acres. Awesome crown molding throughout the residence. Large three car garage with cabinets and a sink  The roof was replaced in 2021 and the seller advised that the warranty is transferable.  This is a must see.
